(25, 'Rambo Extreme Performance R750XPS Electric Bike (Viper Western Camo)', 'The Rambo Extreme Performance R750XPS Electric Bike is lightweight yet strong and powerful. At only 69 pounds this all terrain two-wheeler can carry up to 300lb for over 20 miles on a single charge without pedaling. Its powerful 750W high torque motor is whisper quiet, while its hydraulic disk brakes offer serious stopping power. With 9 different gear settings, up to 5 different power levels and FAT 4 Maxxis this bicycle can take you down the trail or the beach. Rugged and Dependable No costs were spared to build the most extreme off road fat bike. The frame and battery are carbon dippedAand features a custom-built frame to accommodate many different rider sizes and maximize control. Whats more, the R750XPS sports a customizable frame mounting points for tons of accessories to fit your mission. POWERFUL MOTOR: Bafang 750W BBSH02 High Torque Mid Drive motor BRAKES: High performance hydraulic disk brakes for serious stopping power TIRES: Maxxis Minion FBF, FBR 26? x 4.0? fat tire with double wall rim FRAME: Camo frame for ultimate concealment BATTERY: Ride over 20 miles without pedaling with Panasonic 48V 11.6AH battery  - POWERFUL MOTOR: Bafang 750W BBSH02 High Torque Mid Drive motor - BRAKES: High performance hydraulic disk brakes for serious stopping power - TIRES: Maxxis Minion FBF, FBR 26? x 4.0? fat tire with double wall rim - FRAME: Camo frame for ultimate concealment - BATTERY: Ride over 20 miles without pedaling with Panasonic 48V 11.6AH battery', 5, 3699.99, 8, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/21cf4ae9-6d97-420a-b487-46f13dcb57bc.c940f33a8ee0d5f7b5e229c393857897.jpeg?odnWidth=612&odnHeight=612&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
(26, '57 x 30 x 54 in. Spirit MR100 Recumbent Ergometer Bike', 'The MR100s recumbent design pays particular attention to hip and lower body joint mobility, allowing optimal rehabilitation at a relatively relaxed posture. Users may input desired knee flexion angles and the software will suggest the pedal and the seats fore/aft position. Variables such as body symmetry and limb length can be taken into account for clinicians to finely tailor to every patient s needs.The MR100 is equipped with the standard MA900 Rehabilitation Adjustable Crank, which operates in a closed-kinetic chain environment. It is safe, impact free, and pain free within the patients ROM. Features Spirit MR100 Recumbent Ergometer Bike Specifications Dimension: 57 x 30 x 54 Weight: 199 lbs - SKU: ZX9FMSP11822 - Spirit MR100 Recumbent Ergometer Bike - Dimension: 57 x 30 x 54 - Weight: 199 lbs', 6, 3698.9, 16, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/e89eba51-28a8-4dea-b588-d6abd8991991_1.1a90d8509923787b27370661923db6e6.jpeg?odnWidth=612&odnHeight=612&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 1, 0),
(27, 'PhysioStep RXT-1000 Recumbent Elliptical Exercise Machine (Commercial Grade Quality)', 'One of the most innovative pieces of cardio equipment on the market today that you should consider for your gym is the HCI PhysioStep RXT-1000 Recumbent Elliptical Cross Trainer. This machine takes the elliptical machine but puts a recumbent bike feeling on it as youll be seated while performing the motion.This is a great option for those users who do suffer from knee or back pain to an extremely high level as they will get all the benefits that the elliptical has to offer without any stress on their knee or hip joints.This machine is great for your gym because it will offer users both an upper body and lower body workout at the same time, should they choose to use both the handrails and foot pedals, or can be customized to work just the upper or lower body workout on their own.In addition to this, the machine will also offer a great core workout to your users, which is something that many gym members will be seeking.Built to provide high levels of comfort and with the inclusion of a heart rate monitor, this will have everything that your members are looking for.How This Gym Equipment Benefits Your Health ClubOne of the nice things about having this machine in your gym is that you can cut down on other cardio equipment youll purchase such as having both ellipticals and recumbent bikes. Instead, this machine combines both movement patterns to offer a new experience that you can bet your members will enjoy.This machine also allows them to select a workout program to use from eleven different options, so your members will never be bored with their cardio sessions again.Many physiotherapists are now purchasing this machine for their treatment centers, so as a rehabilitation piece of equipment to have, itll be perfect in your gym. Those who are fighting an injury will take great interest in it, so by making an investment in one or two of these, you will really be catering to each and every gym member.The machine also supports a user weight of up to 350 pounds, so any member will definitely be able to use it.Overall, if you bring this machine into your gym you can rest assured that its going to gather a high amount of attention and always be in constant use.Features: Arm System: Multi Position Synchronized Motion . Seat Rail: Extruded Aluminum Indexed Adjustment Pedals: Oversized Pedal Platforms with sure-grip Display: High Resolution Backlit Blue LCD Display with 8 Data Windows Plus a Brickyard Display. Programs: Offers 11 different programming options for complete workout customization include Manual, Rolling Hills, Peak, Plateau, Mountain Climb, Hill Interval, Strength Interval, Fat Burn HRC, Cardio HRC, Custom 1 & Custom 2 Heart Rate: Comes with both a contact and chest strap heart rate monitor so users can track their heart rate at all times Weight Plates: Machine drilled to exact specifications and employ oversize nylon bushings for super-smooth operation. Guide Rods: Highly-polished, chrome plated solid steel guide rods and selector rods for smooth movement to provide you with a comfortable workout at all times.Specifications: Dimensions: 48AL, 32AW, 44AH Max User Weight:350 lbs. Weight: 209 Resistance System: Commercial Resistance Levels:16. Seated Elliptical Stride:12.Warranty:This machine comes with a lifetime warranty for the frame, one year for labor, and three years for parts. PhysioStep RXT-1000 Recumbent Elliptical Exercise Machine (Commercial Grade Quality)', 7, 3567, 16, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/93202306-f443-42f9-854c-b04b08121e1d_1.6c840803d9372efd1fa0077920c7f5ed.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
