(64, 'FTR Caddytrek R2 Robotic Electric Golf Cart Caddy Trek', 'FTR Caddytrek R2 Robotic Electric Golf Cart Caddy Trek. Authorized dealer-warranty is valid. 2015 FTR Caddytrek R2 Robotic Electric Golf Cart Caddy Trek. Authorized dealer-warranty is valid. For a valid warranty please have assembled at your local bike shop. The new R2 offers some improved functionality such as a stronger 5th wheel design and straight line tracking. Improved hardward additions such as a gyroscope keep the unit moving in a staight line over uneven terrain. Watch a short video on straight line tracking on the R2 product announcement post. Additionally, R2 owners will enjoy a coming firmware upgrade that will give their units added functionality, such as Marching Mode and multi-user capability. Marching Mode Go hands free as the unit tracks in front of the player. Clipping the handset into the front waistline allows the user to move forward while the cart maintains distance and angle to the user. In Marching Mode the player never loses sight of their bag or the next tee box. Watch a demonstration video of Marching Mode in action. Multi-user Now team up with fellow CaddyTrek users as a group. The grouping features allows teams to synch their units together to enjoy uninterrupted signal communication among the group. Grouping eliminates signal interference that can sometimes occur from other units, allowing a team of players trouble-free operation of their individual CaddyTrek unit. Product Description The CaddyTrek is a smart robotic golf caddy that carries your bag so you dont have to. The CaddyTrek allows golfers to walk hands free, allowing players to enjoy the health benefits of the game of golf without the burden of carrying a bag. Less fatigue means better levels of concentration and control when driving to the tee or playing the short game. Studies show that walking improves stamina and core strength, and is beneficial to overall fitness in burning calories and building muscle tone. For players who hesitate in walking their round, the CaddyTrek provides a solution to the challenge of managing your gear. Now you can just focus on the game! A rechargeable Lithium Ion battery allows golfers playtime of 27 holes or more on a single charge. The battery charger plugs into a normal household outlet for quick recharging and the folding frame makes for easy storage and transport. Players can store the CaddyTrek easily in the trunk of their car for the drive out to the golf club. The CaddyTrek gives players options with its multi-mode handset. Players can operate the unit in remote, follow, or like a manual push cart. In remote, golfers can send the unit on to the next tee up to a range of 100 feet and at a top speed of 4 mph. When the player attaches the handset to his waistline and initiates follow mode, the unit remains at a distance of 6 paces behind the player, adjusting to the pace of the players stride. Included with the CaddyTrek are the following: 1x A 24v Lithium Ion Battery 1x A Battery Charger 1x A Handset Remote 1x A Handset Battery 1x A Firmware Cable 1x A 1 year of service and support', 13, 1595, 25, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/6368064d-b180-48d5-9ca2-1043cdcb223b_1.aca625e47bc1cd289479a57ed3760a49.png?odnWidth=612&odnHeight=612&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 1, 0),
