(79, 'Spacewalker Black Home Office Walking Treadmill Desk by BodyCraft', 'The Bodycraft Space Walker is a compact treadmill desk that transforms into a piece of ultra modern furniture when youre not using it. While in use, it serves as a very functional work station that allows you to work on your laptop or other device even as you churn through the calories.Experts tell us that we need to be racking up 10,000 steps each day. The Bodycraft Space Walker makes it so much easier to reach that target. It features an extremely solid platform that functions perfectly as a workspace while youre walking. The non slip grip surface is ideal for placing your devices on. A slim-line LCD screen allows you to check your workout progress as youre working. Now you can walk while you work, getting in your 10,000 steps as you meet your daily deadlines.When in exercise mode, this compact treadmill desk will support up to 300 pounds of user weight thanks to its solid platform and wide walking track. With a speed range of between 0.5 and 4.0 miles per hour, it has the power to support any level of walking pace. The motor is labeled at 1.0 horsepower, so theres plenty of grunt here to challenge you and allow for progressive intensity enhancement.The walking belt is a 4-layer antistatic design that provides a smooth, jerk free motion. The shock absorption Elastomer design ensures that every step you take is low impact, avoiding strain on the ankles and knee joints. The LCD screen of the Space Walker folding treadmill provides a bright, red display that is easy to read. It provides real time monitoring of your training speed, time, distance traveled and calories burned. The handle bars feature built in pulse sensors that give immediate feedback regarding your training heart rate. The control buttons on the display are user friendly, with Quick Access Start/Pause, Mode and Speed options.The Bodycraft Space Walker comes with adjustable floor levelers, allowing you to adjust to your flooring to get the ideal level of the walking bed. With a total weight of just 82 pounds, the unit is extremely lightweight and portable. A durable steel frame provides rigidity and durability. And the two carry wheels make easy to wheel the unit away when youre done with your workout. After youve got your daily walking goal, you can quickly and easily fold up the Space Walker with the touch of a buttton. It can then transform into a stylish upright table or bench.With your choice of red and white or black and white, the Space Walker will fit in with any dcor, providing a sturdy, classic piece of furniture from which to serve your guests or simply to put your feet up. Theres even a special compartment for you to store away the power cord when not in use, so that it doesnt interfere with the tables functionality. It truly is the ultimate in space saving efficiency.The Bodycraft Space Walker folding treadmill arrives fully assembled and ready to go.Features: Display: Easy to read bright red LED display Readout: Time, Speed, Distance, Calories, Pulse Button Type: Tactile Membrane (for extended life expectancy) User-Friendly Buttons: Quick-access Start/Pause, Mode & Speed (+/-) & Hold-to-resetSpecs: Speed Range - 0.5-4 mph Walking Surface - 14.6W x 38.6L Roller - 1.5 Diameter Machine steel rollers Deck - Steel reinforced Laminated Melamine 0.5 MDF running deck Belt - 4-layer (1.4mm thick) Antistatic Running Belt User Capacity - 300lbs / 136kgs Assembled Weight / Dimensions - 82lbs - 48L x 22W x 45H Folded Size - 11L x 22W x 45H Shipping Info - 91lbs - 46L x 23W x 13H Handlebar Features - Built-in hand pulse sensors for immediate pulse readout Frame - Durable steel frame under the running deck for durability Leveler - Adjustable floor levelers Wheels - 2 piece transportation wheelsHome Warranty: All Parts -3 years Labor - 90 days Spacewalker Black Home Office Walking Treadmill Desk by BodyCraft', 26, 849, 16, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/d2f8b8c3-af81-46ad-af65-92b1631955d