(107, 'RECSOUL Folding Treadmill Electric ,A6 Multi-function Treadmill for Home 500W Motorized Power Running Machine with Bluetooth', 'Description: Low Noise Workout Experience Acoustical Material Running Belt of treadmill, and 2.5 Peak HP super-quiet motor(<60DB), freely enjoy the ultra quiet running experience with no need to worry about disturbing others at night. Max User Weight Capacity Support max 240 lbs weight capacity for users. Start losing weight without struggle. Roomy Walking Belt and Deck 1020mm*400mm walking belt, 560mm wide deck can let you fully stretch. No misstep, no dropping off, no falling! Multi-layered cushioning system 7 layers of belt cushion + Cushioned deck + built-in motor damper make it easy on your knees and joints when running. Variable Speed Motor One touch control, 12 speed settings(1.0 kph to 12.0 kph)for free choice: 1 to 3 kph: walking 4 to 6 kph: hiking 6 to 9 kph: marathon 9 to 12 kph: Sprinting SpaceSaver Design Easy assembly and foldable design, takes only 0.5m2 when folded. Double Safety Protection Design Treadmill handlebars provide a grip when runners lose balance on the treadmill. In case of falling down, the treadmill will stop working with the magnetic safety lock off the spot. Just enjoy your worry-free workout. Not just A Normal Treadmill for Running Multi-function design, support performing different types of workout simultaneously. When one is running on the belt, the other can do stretch using a pulling strap. Perform a happy exercise time with your lover! Specifications: 1) Color: Black 2) Multi-function three-layer dumbbell stand, Electric massage head is included. 3) Running belt area: 40*102cm 4) Running platform width: 56cm wide 5) Expanded size: 148*65*125cm 6) Folding size: 138*71*24cm 7) Peak horsepower: 2.5P HP , 500W 8) Maximum load bearing: 110 kg 9) Speed range: 1.0-12.8km/h RESOUL Folding Treadmill,A6 Multiple Function Treadmill with Bluetooth', 50, 459.99, 16, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/45de195a