(157, 'Efitment Swift Magnetic Indoor Cycle Bike', 'Stay on the cutting edge of fitness when you ride the IC035 EFITMENT Swift Magnetic Indoor Cycle Bike. Mount this durable and sleek exercise bike with confidence as you slip your feet into the secure foot pedals with adjustable straps. Start your ride by adjusting the tension knob located on the side of the bike, to move through 8 levels of smooth magnetic resistance as you complete each belt driven revolution of the 13.2-pound flywheel. This low maintenance exercise machine comes with a 4-way adjustable seat and height adjustable handlebars to give you a personalized fit for optimal workout performance. Easy to use foot levelers help keep your bike firmly against the floor as you push through intense workouts. The 27.5-inch to 37.7-inch inseam range allows users of different heights to ride comfortably. The multi-grip, non-slip handlebars make it easy to transition through multiple hands positions. The AAA battery-powered meter display and hand pulse sensors provide accurate distance and heart rate readings. Add a personalized touch to your workouts with the tablet and device holder. Stop your ride safely with the centered red emergency brake. The integrated transportation wheels make this indoor bike easy to move while not in use. With a max user weight of 265 pounds, this cycle bike will help you train like a champion. Push yourself to the limit with the IC035 Swift Magnetic Indoor Cycle Bike by EFITMENT. 8 LEVELS OF MAGNETIC RESISTANCE A 8 Levels of micro adjustable magnetic resistance keeps your ride smooth while providing increased resistance as your ride strength increases. MULTI ADJUSTABLE SEAT AND HANDLEBARS A Create your perfect riding position with the multi adjustable seat and handle bars.A SMOOTH BELT DRIVE RESISTANCEA The smooth feel of the belt drive mechanism paired with its sturdy construction creates optimal feel with low maintenance performance.A DEVICE HOLDER A The integrated personal device hol