(200, '26 Firmstrong Bruiser Man Single Speed Beach Cruiser Mens Bicycle, Matte Black with Orange Rims', 'Designed to be classic yet masculine, Firmstrongs 26-Inch Single-Speed Bruiser Man Beach Bike is a favorite among men and is truly a guys guy beach cruiser bike. A great fit for most men from 5 feet, 4 inches to 6 feet, 4 inches tall, its ideal for recreational Beach Cruiser Bike riding as well as exercise and commuting. The 4-inch extended frame length provides more space between you and the handlebars. The curved 19-inch steel cruiser frame design features a thick, beefy top tube design, while the 26-inch aluminum wheels with 2.125-inch wide all black tires roll smooth and easy as well as cushion the bumps as you ride over them freely. The wide, oversized saddle seat completes your comfort with dual springs that help make the ride soft and cushy. Both the seat and the handlebars can be adjusted for height and tilt to ensure maximum comfort. Whenever you need to stop you simply pedal backwards, easing on the coaster brake. Other features of the Firmstrong Bruiser Man Beach Cruiser Bike for Men include wide Beach Cruiser handlebars with synthetic leather grips, waffle tread tires and, a guard to protect pant cuffs from getting caught in the chain. All of Firmstrongs Beach Cruisers are shipped 80 percent assembled. Firmstrong has been designing high quality, affordable Beach Bikes for over 10 years with a focus on blending style and functionality to create a fun, adventurous experience for riders -- not just a mode of transportation. Whats included in the box? Your bicycle frame, the front/rear wheels and saddle, a hardware box including pedals and reflectors, and an assembly instruction manual. Each bike comes 85% assembled. This means, front wheel, pedals, seat and handlebars need to be installed by customer. Some adjustment may be required on gears and brakes. If a customized bike, all accessories purchased will need to be installed. This includes baskets, cup