ent visual tool Steel shaft Durable and comfortable for walking golfers Easily straps to any type of cart Auto deploy kick out leg stand 7-way padded top to keep your clubs organized Large storage pockets are spacious and easily accessible Color: Gold Manufacturer warranty: 1-year warranty  - Mens left-handed 15-piece golf club set - Standard length recommended for 5 feet 5 inches to 6 feet 1 inch - Powerful design focuses all specs to deliver distance and control - Distance engineered for faster swing speeds - Matching head covers for driver, fairway wood, and hybrid - Large sweet spot features power weighting and strong lofts for greater distance - 10.5 degree w/ flex graphite shaft - Strong loft and low weighting creates a long distance club from fairway or rough - Large sweet spot with tip reinforced flex graphite shaft - Easy to hit and replaces old hard to hit long irons - Improved high launch design produces more hang time resulting in longer, straighter shots - True temper steel shaft - Extreme perimeter weighting creates enormous sweet spot for more forgiveness - Rugged stainless steel irons with low torque steel shafts - Enhanced spin technology in this versatile wedge - Improves playability and performance on the green - Designed with super low weighting and a wide sole - Helps launch the ball from the bunker - Heel/toe weighted design improves putter head stability - Easy alignment visual tool - Steel shaft - Durable and comfortable for walking golfers - Easily straps to any type of cart - Auto deploy kick out leg stand - 7-way padded top to keep your clubs organized - Large storage pockets are spacious and easily accessible - Color: Gold - Manufacturer warranty: 1-year warranty', 65, 199.99, 27, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/eb9666e7-ce66-4762-943e-40ccc10d2702_1.a31b9c76a6045be70b511f0dbb9e1d6b.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
