(261, 'T-Fight 305 XTC Tennis Racquet', 'Tecnifibre has updated one of their most prominent player frames on the market in the Tecnifibre T-Fight 305 XTC Tennis Racquet. Now a partner with Lacoste, the look of the T-Fights has a decidedly stylish look. The new T-Fights incorporate Xtreme Touch Construction, mix of graphite, alloy, and polyester fibers to increase frame strength and allow greater flexibility. Dynacore HD returns to provide a soft feel without sacrificing power. Tecnifibre has improved their EZ Lock+ grommets to make the tie off holes last longer, and the re-stringing easier. The Horse Back grommets are updated to reduce string breakage on off-center hits, and the Armor Cap (head guard) increases protection by 40% without adding weight. The 305 offers solid stability at about 11.2 oz strung. The 98` head and 18x19 string pattern provide plenty of control, and the Headlight balance assures fast swing speed and access to spin. T-Fight 305 XTC Tennis Racquet', 137, 199.95, 18, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/c48148b6-a67e-4f7b-9601-e0bf6529b519_1.19004a3cb6da8a4cf8970082f5a2e9cc.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
