(265, 'Graphene 360 Radical MP Tennis Racquet', 'HEAD`s newest Radical MP Tennis Racquet adds Graphene 360 as the structural base of the frame. The technology reinforces the racquet in the shaft and it extends all the way up through the racquet head for improved stability and greater energy transfer. HEAD improved on the previous generations Graphene Touch technology and built a more comfortable Radical MP for the aggressive and creative shot maker. The Graphene 360 Radical MP has the familiar 20/23/21 mm beam width and HEAD`s Dynamic 16 x 19 string pattern that spaces out the cross strings for better access to spin and power. The MP is the most versatile in the Radical series at 11 ounces strung, and is the optimum choice for players seeking controllable power. The asymmetric design identity uses creative color-blocking to present a more subtle and sophisticated look than the brighter versions of the past few generations. The MP offers a moderate swing weight and won`t get pushed around during big hitting exchanges but is still very mobile. HEAD continues the strong lineage of the Radical line with a comfortable, rock-solid Graphene 360 Radical MP. Graphene 360 Radical MP Tennis Racquet', 138, 194.95, 18, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/8d651156-949d-472e-8657-4abd53a5a077.b4f6c7337ca9f2f487a99eb6983ab13b.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
