(269, 'adidas Adult Classic Pro Fingersave Soccer Goalkeeper Gloves', 'Pay tribute to the generations that have paved the way for the modern game as you sport the throwback design of the adidas Adult Classic Pro Soccer Goalkeeper Gloves. Utilizing premium Nova latex for consistent ball control and a lightweight flexible feel, these gloves deliver maximum mobility and a cushioned, snug fit when taking stance inside the posts. Comfortable Feel, Consistent Grip Negative cut provides a snug fit for consistent speed and natural movement Latex gussets deliver maximum mobility and an unmatched, seamless touch Close-fitting bandage with no restrictive seams offers a snug fit Durable Defense Fingersave spines prevent potential hyperextensions when executing parries for maximized protection 4mm cushioning has been tried and tested on all adidas balls to absorb impact Key Details Palm: Nova latex Cut: Negative Materials: 53% Latex, 15% Polyurethane, 12% Cotton, 20% Other 0', 142, 191.15, 15, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/5b3af419-063a-47be-b126-b6f9501555d2_1.5d5e4f172a0940000e24ab2898edfa10.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
