(418, 'Team Speed White Blue Prestrung Tennis Racquet', 'Offering a very sleek orange and black cosmetic, the Volkl Team Speed Tennis Racquet in Blue and White is loaded with pop and playabiltiy. With a generous sweetspot from its 102 square-inch headsize, this racquet offers power and comfort from all areas of the court. A maneuverable weight and balance makes it easy for players to develop the swing speeds necessary for spin, pace and depth. The open 16x19 string pattern provides plenty of bite and provides a lively feel. At net the racquet continues to feel maneuverable. The feel is crisp and precise with ample control to go along with the impressive power. On serve the maneuverable response shines through. Both spin and pace are easy to generate and the healthy sweetspot promotes consistent hitting. Priced at a great value, this one offers big performance for stronger beginners through intermediate level players. This racquet comes prestrung. Team Speed White Blue Prestrung Tennis Racquet', 122, 109.99, 18, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/62c8798d-9765-4552-a5e8-4b06c7daf4bb_1.850f19d592e4a49df1819c606287e2d7.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
(419, 'New Orange Whip Golf Swing Training Aid 44 Length Trainer 853279004084', 'Designed for those under 5 6 tall or beginners. Recommended for Men, Women, Teens, and Seniors 44 inches in total length, approximately 41 actual swing length (Mens Mid-Iron/ Ladies Driver). The total weight is 1.76 pounds. Simulates Mid-Iron motion and Ladies Driver motion. This model is more manageable to swing because it is shorter than the Full sized Trainer. Provides some Core Fitness and Flexibility. Ideal Whip for most Women and Senior golfers to improve their Balance and Tempo. The Golden Whip is universal for both men and women. Easiest to use for most seniors, women, beginners and shorter players.Swinging the Golden is most similar to swinging a long iron or hybrid.The Golden shaft is shorter and slightly stiffer, which allows for faster transitions. Gender: Male Material: Rubber  - Designed for those under 5 6 tall or beginners. Recommended for Men, Women, Teens, and Seniors - 44 inches in total length, approximately 41 actual swing length (Mens Mid-Iron/ Ladies Driver). - The total weight is 1.76 pounds. - Simulates Mid-Iron motion and Ladies Driver motion. This model is more manageable to swing because it is shorter than the Full sized Trainer. Provides some Core Fitness and Flexibility. - Ideal Whip for most Women and Senior golfers to improve their Balance and Tempo. - Gender: Male - Material: Rubber', 209, 109.98, 29, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/aaf9cd4f-e8a1-4164-8a3f-a1771c585399.b97c88944e2b7a5bb1f1f5dcc5633731.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
(420, 'Graphene Touch Speed Pro Tennis Racquet', 'ATP world #1 Novak Djokovic continues his partnership with HEADs newest technology by endorsing the Speed Series. The Graphene Touch Speed Pro was engineered with the worlds strongest and lightest material to make their Graphene Touch racquets 30%* stronger providing an optimized weight distribution for a faster swing and more power. By using graphene Touch in the racquet shaft, HEAD has been able to dampen the vibration produced by the racquet giving the racquet power that never felt so good! Make no mistake, however: this continues to be a control stick for aggressive players. All the great Speed control factors are still here, including narrow beams, standard length, strong weight, and head light balance. The dense 18 x 20 string pattern and midplus 100 square inch head size will help even the biggest hitters control their power and topspin throughout the court. If you play an aggressive baseline game like Djokovic, the Graphene Touch Speed Pro should be at the top of your demo list. See which top 20 players used this racquet in Melbourne in our blog post, `The HEAD Graphene Touch Series in the 2018 Australian Open.` ATP world 1 Novak Djokovic continues his partnership with HEADs newest technology by endorsing the Speed Series The Graphene Touch Speed Pro was engineered with the worlds strongest and lightest material to make their Graphene Touch racquets 30 stronger providing an optimized weight distribution for a faster swing and more power By using graphene Touch in the racquet shaft HEAD has been able to dampen the vibration produced by the racquet giving the racquet power that never felt so good Make no mistake however this continues to be a control stick for aggressive players All the great Speed control factors are still here including narrow beams standard length strong weight and head light balance The dense 18 x 20 string pattern and midplus 100 square inch head size will help even the biggest hitters control their power and topspin throughout the court If you play an aggressive baseline game like Djokovic the Graphene Touch Speed Pro should be at the top of your demo list', 138, 109.95, 18, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/5384a0c4-9494-4a29-8289-57f3c6439c08_1.7a8df973444ac49334c057525b6886eb.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
