evaTear innovation - Great for strength training, heavy power punches, and endurance - Color: Black - Dimensions (L x Dia): 53 x 13.25 inches - Weight: 100 pounds - Manufacturer warranty: 120-day warranty', 236, 93.99, 9, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/5cf8fec5-61ee-47ca-96ad-38ca5416e108_1.5abc3f77ce30eac72957938d3c0ed846.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
(474, 'BSTWVP40 40lb Premium Adjustable Weighted Vest', 'Take your training to the next level with Body-Solids BSTWVP40 40lb Weight Vest. Specially designed to withstand the toughest workouts, the BSTWVP40 features durable stitching to ensure long-lasting use. The BSTWVP40 is fully adjustable and allows you customize weight and resistance up to 40lbs. Customizing the vest is simple and easy A add or remove sand bags from the pouches in the vest to achieve the exact workout you desire. Premium fabrics guarantee a comfortable fit while the sandbag weights provide a flexible weight option that perfectly conforms to your body. The BSTWVP40s two adjustable straps are wider than standard weight vests and feature durable Velcro to reduce vest movement during workouts and allow for proper placement of the weights, resulting in optimal center of gravity without restricting any type of range of motion. Body-Solid BSTWVP40 40lb Weight Vest is perfect for a multitude of markets and fitness goals from sports performance training, cross/functional training, rehab and more. TECH SPECS: Premium, durable stitching Adjustable up to 40 lbs. Fast and easy weight customization Flexible sandbag weights conform to body Two Velcro straps ensure perfect fit', 158, 93.56, 12, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/d13341b2-6798-4570-b622-627241620cf1_1.1382cfbb3a9d01f86f45006ddf4729b4.jpeg?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
(475, '2021 Hyperlite State 2.0 Boat Wakeboard', 'Creating a shape to take riders\' skills to the next level was the goal behind the new State 2.0. Learning from other asymmetrical designs, Hyperlite found that creating a shorter but more effective edge on a rider\'s toe-side made hard to learn wake jumps that much easier. This is because there is less rail to initiate when applying toe-side pressure. Once set, the smoother toe-side transition is then held by the State 2.0\'s thinner profile molded-in fin, creating less drag and a better release off the top of the wake. Subtle Toe-Side Footbed Risers were also added to help a rider create more leverage when pressure is applied. The longer, more traditional heel-side edge compliments this asymmetrical design by allowing the natural body position of a rider to generate stability and speed into the wake without a loss of pop due to reduced surface area.\r\n\r\nThe State 2.0 has been tested and proven to be the best choice for a rider looking to master the foundations of wakeboarding.', 102, 279, 22, 'https://www.s2as.com/Images/ExtraLarge/610f2483-284f-487d-8014-60225d5a1b23.jpg', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 1, 0),
