(870, 'Dual-Surface Hitting/Practice, Chipping and Driving Golf Grass Mat with Fairway and Rough Surfaces', 'The key to playing good golf is developing a consistent, dependable swing. This only comes with practice. Made of high-quality nylon grass, the Dual Surface hitting mat by ProActive Sports provides realistic on course simulation for a variety of shots and clubs, while maintaining a life-like feel. The sturdy construction is built to last and can be used indoors or outdoors. The dual-surfaces and two tee positions provide plenty of shot options. Practice drives from the tee (included), iron shots from the fairway, or chipping from the rough on the same mat. With a hitting area of 1 x 2 you have plenty of room to practice, yet its compact for easy storage. Dual-level surfaces allow you to practice your drives, iron shots, and short game from the same mat with true on-course simulation and life-like feel.Made of durable, high-quality, nylon grass built to last with heavy-duty rubber backing for indoor or outdoor use.Fairway surface simulates the feel of closely-mown grass, while the longer surface replicates rough-like conditions. Perfect for beginners or advanced players alike.Overall Mat Dimensions: 1 foot x 2 feet.Includes one 1-1/2 rubber tee with two tee positions.', 357, 32.02, 29, 'https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/e1203c57-381d-45af-a1a1-75e1fd20be33_4.63b72604ca13d5591f69b73435c3e1ba.png?odnWidth=undefined&odnHeight=undefined&odnBg=ffffff', '2021-04-01', '2021-04-01', 0, 0),
